data.description: Charming 3 bed 2 bath home in the heart of Snelling. This home has been well maintained. Spacious kitchen with tile floors.  Bedrooms and bathrooms have ample space.  One car garage provides parking and or a great shop setup, nice backyard with plenty of space for entertaining and side yard with a storage shed. Close to parks and school. Come check it out!
